<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">About Payxem</div>
    <h1 class="headline-lg">Getting Paid Should<br>Be Simple</h1>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Payxem was built to solve a problem many freelancers know too well — getting paid should be simple, but for millions of people, it is not.
    </p>
    <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin-top: 12px;">
      In many countries, access to global payment systems like PayPal and Stripe is limited or unavailable. This creates a gap between skilled professionals and the clients who are ready to pay them.
    </p>
    <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin-top: 12px;">
      <strong>Payxem bridges that gap.</strong>
    </p>
    <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin-top: 12px;">
      It is a simple invoicing and payment platform that allows freelancers, entrepreneurs, and small businesses to create invoices, share payment links, and receive payments from clients worldwide. Clients can pay using familiar methods like cards, Apple Pay, Google Pay, or PayPal, while users receive their earnings through accessible local options.
    </p>
    <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin-top: 12px;">
      The goal is not to replace existing systems, but to make them work for people who have been left out.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

