      <h2>Why Payxem Exists</h2>
      <p>For years, freelancers have relied on workarounds — using third parties, informal networks, or complex setups just to receive payments.</p>
      <p>These solutions are not sustainable.</p>
      <p>Payxem was created to offer a more reliable and structured approach, giving users a professional way to bill clients and manage payments without unnecessary barriers.</p>
